                <h1>Easy Guide: Peel and Stick Wallpaper Over Paneling</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper is an easy and stylish solution for updating paneled walls. It's a DIY-friendly option that requires minimal prep work. Clean the surface, measure your panels, and cut the wallpaper to size. With its adhesive backing, simply peel and apply, smoothing out air bubbles for a flawless finish. Transform any room effortlessly!</p>
